<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.176630>
    dc:description "FIGURES 4 A – H. Chilicola catamarcense Packer, n. sp. Male head: A. frontal view, B. lateral view. Female head: C. frontal view, D. lateral view. E. surface sculpture of mesoscutum and scutellum of male. F. Hind leg of male. G – H. Male genitalia: G. dorsal view to left and ventral view to the right, H. lateral view. Stippling in A and F indicates pale colouration, in G and H membranous regions." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/176630/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

